{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"zettel.20260420055738","title":"Software architecture adalah jaringan keputusan trade-off, bukan sekadar diagram","desc":"Inti software architecture adalah keputusan signifikan yang mencatat konteks, trade-off, dan alasan, bukan hanya struktur sistem.","tags":["permanent-note","software-architecture","architecture","decision-making"],"custom":{},"fname":"zettel.20260420055738","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"e95b1ba16d4c162d9e2b0ab7935950a3","updated":1776914280146,"created":1776914280146,"links":[{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420055738","id":"zettel.20260420055738","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.permanent-note","alias":"permanent-note","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.permanent-note"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420055738","id":"zettel.20260420055738","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.software-architecture","alias":"software-architecture","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.software-architecture"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420055738","id":"zettel.20260420055738","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.architecture","alias":"architecture","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.architecture"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420055738","id":"zettel.20260420055738","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.decision-making","alias":"decision-making","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.decision-making"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420055738","id":"zettel.20260420055738","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.literature.architecture-decision-records","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":18,"offset":1164},"end":{"line":22,"column":69,"offset":1215},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.architecture-decision-records"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":3,"offset":1836},"end":{"line":30,"column":28,"offset":1861},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420055738"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060847","id":"zettel.20260420060847","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":3,"offset":1189},"end":{"line":20,"column":28,"offset":1214},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420055738"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260421161001","id":"zettel.20260421161001","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":79,"column":3,"offset":4935},"end":{"line":79,"column":28,"offset":4960},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420055738"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.architecture-decision-records","id":"zettel.literature.architecture-decision-records","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":52,"column":3,"offset":2579},"end":{"line":52,"column":28,"offset":2604},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420055738"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.architecture-important-stuff","id":"zettel.literature.architecture-important-stuff","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":3,"offset":1016},"end":{"line":21,"column":28,"offset":1041},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420055738"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.internal-quality-is-speed","id":"zettel.literature.internal-quality-is-speed","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":3,"offset":835},"end":{"line":21,"column":28,"offset":860},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420055738"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide","id":"zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":51,"column":3,"offset":3886},"end":{"line":51,"column":28,"offset":3911},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420055738"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","id":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":3,"offset":266},"end":{"line":8,"column":28,"offset":291},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420055738"}],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"software-architecture-adalah-jaringan-keputusan-trade-off-bukan-sekadar-diagram\">Software architecture adalah jaringan keputusan trade-off, bukan sekadar diagram<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#software-architecture-adalah-jaringan-keputusan-trade-off-bukan-sekadar-diagram\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Software architecture paling berguna ketika dia mengekspresikan keputusan dan trade-off yang mendasari struktur, bukan ketika dia hanya memetakan komponen.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Catatan gue:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Banyak tim mengira arsitektur adalah diagram dan komponen. Padahal arsitektur sejatinya adalah keputusan tentang batasan, interaksi, dan kualitas.</li>\n<li>Diagram seperti C4 membantu menjelaskan \"apa\" yang ada. ADR dan decision log menjelaskan \"kenapa\" arah itu dipilih.</li>\n<li>Jika arsitektur tidak menyimpan alasan, artinya tim kehilangan konteks penting ketika sistem berevolusi.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Implikasi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Software architecture harus dilengkapi dengan catatan keputusan seperti ADR, pattern, dan trade-off.</li>\n<li>Keputusan arsitektur yang baik punya batasan scope: hanya hal-hal yang berdampak pada tim, operasional, atau kualitas jangka panjang.</li>\n<li>Tim harus menghubungkan artefak: diagram, ADR, issue, PR, dan implementation guide.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Contoh hubungan:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>diagram C4 menggambarkan struktur service dan boundary,</li>\n<li>ADR menjelaskan mengapa boundary itu ada, opsi yang ditolak, dan kapan keputusan harus dievaluasi ulang,</li>\n<li>trade-off note membantu tim memahami rasa dari akibat keputusan tersebut.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>→ Dikuatkan oleh <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.architecture-decision-records\">Architecture Decision Record — Martin Fowler</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">permanent-note (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">software-architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">decision-making (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420060847\">Arsitektur adalah penentu biaya perubahan masa depan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421161001\">AI-native adalah jargon strategi yang menandai asumsi desain AI sebagai fondasi, bukan sekadar fitur tambahan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.architecture-decision-records\">Architecture Decision Record — Martin Fowler</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.architecture-important-stuff\">Arsitektur adalah apa yang paling penting, bukan hanya struktur tinggi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.internal-quality-is-speed\">Kualitas internal adalah infrastruktur kecepatan delivery</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide\">Software Architecture Guide — Fowler: arsitektur sebagai keputusan penting dan mahal kalau salah</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.software-architecture\">MOC: Software Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomai